cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

The paper proposes a novel descriptor for 3D local shape description and partial shape matching, which is relevant to computer vision (cs.CV) and computer graphics (cs.GR). The descriptor is also applicable to object/scene reconstruction and 3D object recognition, which are related to robotics (cs.RO) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI).
